headline.main: Overall World Cup Winner Hirscher Wraps Up 4th Slalom Title
headline.print_headline: Overall World Cup Winner Hirscher Wraps Up 4th Slalom Title

lead_paragraph: Overall World Cup champion Marcel Hirscher wrapped up his fourth slalom title Sunday with Austrian compatriot Michael Matt winning the penultimate race of the season.
